org.cytoscape.dyn.internal.layout
Interface DynLayout<T>

Type Parameters:
T -
All Known Implementing Classes:
DynLayoutImpl
public interface DynLayout<T>

DynLayout is the interface to represent the dynamics in time of a CyNetworkView and is implemented by DynLayoutImpl.

Author:
Sabina Sara Pfister
